#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose help text for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Market
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/postload.lua:23 input:23 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "A market enables trading with other tribes."
msgstr "Un mercat permet comerciar amb altres tribus."

#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/postload.lua:46 input:46 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Of course hunting crocodiles is a good idea. The efficiency of hunting "
"should not increase much but the productivity can increase, if there are not "
"enough animals in the nearby forests."
msgstr ""
"Per descomptat, caçar cocodrils és una bona idea. L'eficiència de la caça no "
"hauria d'augmentar molt però la productivitat pot augmentar, si no hi ha "
"prou animals als boscos propers."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Atlantean production site: Crocodile Hunter’s House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/postload.lua:49 input:49 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Hunter advocates the idea of building a crocodile hunter's house"
msgstr "Hunter defensa la idea de construir la casa d'un caçador de cocodrils"

#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/postload.lua:50 input:50 standard
msgid ""
"Hunts animals to produce meat. Hunters working at this house can hunt "
"crocodiles too."
msgstr ""
"Caça animals per produir carn. Els caçadors que treballen en aquesta casa "
"també poden caçar cocodrils."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Atlantean production site: Crocodile Hunter’s House, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/postload.lua:53 input:53 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"This building is useful only when you have a Sumatran opponent and there are "
"crocodiles coming from his territory into your territory."
msgstr ""
"Aquest edifici només és útil quan tens un oponent de Sumatra i hi ha "
"cocodrils que vénen del seu territori al teu territori."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Atlantean production site: Crocodile Hunter’s House, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/postload.lua:55 input:55 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"The building has 2 different working areas, the smaller for crocodile "
"hunting and the larger for game hunting."
msgstr ""
"L'edifici té 2 zones de treball diferents, la més petita per a la caça de "
"cocodrils i la més gran per a la caça."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Atlantean production site: Crocodile Hunter’s House, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/postload.lua:59 input:59 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If there is a sufficient amount of crocodiles and other animals, the hunters "
"need %1$s on average to produce one meat. If there are no crocodiles, the "
"building operates as a basic hunter's house and the hunters need %2$s on "
"average to produce one meat."
msgstr ""
"Si hi ha una quantitat suficient de cocodrils i altres animals, els caçadors "
"necessiten de mitjana %1$s per produir una carn. Si no hi ha cocodrils, "
"l'edifici funciona com a casa bàsica de caçadors i els caçadors necessiten "
"de mitjana %2$s per produir una carn."

