#. TRANSLATORS: This is the tooltip for the "Basics" starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/basic_outpost.lua:13
#: input:13 standard
msgid ""
"Start the game with your headquarters and a small selection of wares - just "
"enough to create a few tools to help establish a full economy. Warning: the "
"AI can’t successfully start from this."
msgstr ""
"Comença la partida amb el quarter general i una selecció petita de béns, els "
"suficients per a crear algunes eines i poder establir una economia completa. "
"Avís: amb la posició inicial que té, la IA no té èxit."

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the name of a starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/castaways.lua:11
#: input:11 standard
msgid "Castaways"
msgstr "Nàufrags"

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the tooltip for the "Castaways" starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/castaways.lua:13
#: input:13 standard
msgid ""
"Start the game with one ships on the ocean, the bare minimum of ware and few "
"workers. Warning: the AI can’t successfully start from this. You will need "
"to find a portspace with direct access to rocks and trees. For unknown maps, "
"game without fog of war recommended."
msgstr ""
"Comença el joc amb un vaixell a l'oceà, el mínim de mercaderies i pocs "
"treballadors. Avís: la IA no pot començar amb èxit a partir d'això. Haureu "
"de trobar un espai portuari amb accés directe a roques i arbres. Per a mapes "
"desconeguts, es recomana el joc sense boira de guerra."

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the name of a starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/discovery.lua:11
#: input:11 standard
msgid "Discovery"
msgstr "Descoberta"

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the tooltip for the "Discovery" starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/discovery.lua:13
#: input:13 standard
msgid ""
"Start the game with three ships on the ocean and only a handful of supplies"
msgstr ""
"Comença el joc amb tres vaixells a l'oceà i només un grapat de "
"subministraments"

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the name of a starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/fortified_village.lua:11
#: input:11 standard
msgid "Fortified Village"
msgstr ""

