#. TRANSLATORS: This is the tooltip for the "New World" starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/new_world.lua:13
#: input:13 standard
msgid "Start the game with seven ships full of wares on the ocean"
msgstr "Comença el joc amb set vaixells plens de mercaderies a l'oceà"

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the name of a starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/poor_hamlet.lua:11
#: input:11 standard
msgid "Poor Hamlet"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the tooltip for the "Poor Hamlet" (minimum) starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/poor_hamlet.lua:13
#: input:13 standard
msgid ""
"Start the game with just a warehouse and the bare minimum for bootstrapping "
"an economy. Warning: the AI can’t successfully start from this."
msgstr ""
"Comença el joc amb només un magatzem i el mínim necessari per iniciar una "
"economia. Avís: la IA no pot començar amb èxit a partir d'això."

#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/poor_hamlet.lua:49
#: input:49 standard
msgid "Be careful"
msgstr "Aneu amb compte"

#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/poor_hamlet.lua:49
#: input:49 standard
msgid ""
"You have only one iron for each tool you will need to start your economy. "
"Make sure no unneeded tool is created."
msgstr ""
"Només teniu una planxa per a cada eina que necessitareu per iniciar la "
"vostra economia. Assegureu-vos que no es creï cap eina innecessària."

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the name of a starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/struggling_outpost.lua:11
#: input:11 standard
msgid "Struggling Outpost"
msgstr "Post de mercaderies en dificultats"

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the tooltip for the "Hardcore" starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/struggling_outpost.lua:13
#: input:13 standard
msgid ""
"Start the game with just your headquarters and very few wares for "
"bootstrapping an economy. Warning: the AI can’t successfully start from this."
msgstr ""
"Comenceu la partida només amb un quarter general i molts pocs béns per "
"desenvolupar l'economia. Avís: les IA poden no desenvolupar-se adequadament "
"si comencen amb aquesta condició inicial."

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the name of a starting condition
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/scripting/starting_conditions/tidy_warehouses.lua:13
#: input:13 standard
