#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Granite, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:108
#: input:108 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Granite is a basic building material."
msgstr "El granit és un material bàsic de construcció."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Granite, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:110
#: input:110 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid "The Atlanteans produce granite blocks in quarries and crystal mines."
msgstr ""
"Els atlants produeixen blocs de granit en pedreres i mines de cristall."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Log, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:120
#: input:120 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid ""
"Logs are an important basic building material. They are produced by felling "
"trees."
msgstr ""
"Els troncs són un material bàsic de construcció important. Es produeixen per "
"tala d'arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Log, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:122
#: input:122 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Atlanteans use logs also as the base for planks, which are used in nearly "
"every building. Besides the sawmill, the charcoal kiln, the toolsmithy and "
"the smokery also need logs for their work."
msgstr ""
"Els atlantes utilitzen troncs també com a base per a taulons, que "
"s'utilitzen en gairebé tots els edificis. A més de la serradora, la "
"carbonera, la ferreria i el fumador també necessiten troncs per a la seva "
"feina."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Planks, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:133
#: input:133 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Planks are an important building material."
msgstr "Els taulons són un material de construcció important."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Planks, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:135
#: input:135 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid "They are produced out of logs by the sawmill."
msgstr "Són produïts a partir de troncs per la serradora."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Planks, part 3
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:137
#: input:137 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"The weapon smithy and the shipyard also use planks to produce the different "
"tridents and mighty ships."
msgstr ""
"La ferreria d'armes i la drassana també utilitzen taulons per produir els "
"diferents tridents i vaixells poderosos."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Spider Silk
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:147
#: input:147 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Spider silk is produced by spiders, which are bred by spider farms. It can "
"be processed into spidercloth or tabards in a weaving mill, or used to make "
"tools in the toolsmithy."
msgstr ""
"La seda d'aranya és produïda per aranyes, que són criades per granges "
"d'aranya. Es pot processar en tela d'aranya o tabards en una fàbrica de "
"teixits, o utilitzar-se per fer eines a la ferreria."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Spidercloth
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:156
#: input:156 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Spidercloth is made out of spider silk in a weaving mill. It is used in the "
"shipyard. Also some higher developed buildings need spidercloth for their "
"construction."
msgstr ""
"La tela d'aranya està feta de seda d'aranya en una fàbrica de teixits. "
"S'utilitza a la drassana. També alguns edificis més desenvolupats necessiten "
"tela d'aranya per a la seva construcció."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Fish
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:167
#: input:167 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Fish is one of the biggest food resources of the Atlanteans. It has to be "
"smoked in a smokery before being delivered to mines, training sites and "
"scouts."
msgstr ""
"El peix és un dels recursos alimentaris més importants dels atlants. S'ha de "
"fumar en un fumador abans de ser lliurat a les mines, llocs d'entrenament i "
"exploradors."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Smoked Fish
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:176
#: input:176 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"As no Atlantean likes raw fish, smoking it in a smokery is the most common "
"way to make it edible."
msgstr ""
"Com que a cap atlante li agrada el peix cru, fumar-lo en un fumat és la "
"forma més habitual de fer-lo comestible."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Meat, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:185
#: input:185 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid ""
"Meat contains a lot of energy, and it is obtained from wild game taken by "
"hunters or from seashells collected by fishers."
msgstr ""
"La carn conté molta energia, i s'obté de la caça salvatge presa pels "
"caçadors o de les petxines recollides pels pescadors."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Meat, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:187
#: input:187 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Meat has to be smoked in a smokery before being delivered to mines and "
"training sites (dungeon, labyrinth and temple)."
msgstr ""
"La carn s'ha de fumar en un fumat abans de ser lliurada a les mines i llocs "
"d'entrenament (masmorra, laberint i temple)."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Smoked Meat
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:197
#: input:197 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Smoked meat is made out of meat in a smokery. It is delivered to the mines "
"and training sites (labyrinth, dungeon and temple) where the miners and "
"soldiers prepare a nutritious lunch for themselves."
msgstr ""
"La carn fumada es fa amb carn en un fumat. Es lliura a les mines i llocs "
"d'entrenament (laberint, calabós i temple) on els miners i soldats preparen "
"un dinar nutritiu per a ells mateixos."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Water, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:206
#: input:206 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Water is the essence of life!"
msgstr "L'aigua és essencial per a la vida!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Water, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:208
#: input:208 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid "Water is used in the bakery and the horse and spider farms."
msgstr "L'aigua s'utilitza a la fleca i a les granges de cavalls i aranyes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Corn
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:217
#: input:217 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"This corn is processed in the mill into fine cornmeal that every Atlantean "
"baker needs for a good bread. Also horse and spider farms need to be "
"provided with corn."
msgstr ""
"Aquest blat de moro es processa al molí en farina de blat de moro fina que "
"tot forner d'Atlantes necessita per a un bon pa. També cal proveir de blat "
"de moro les granges de cavalls i aranyes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Cornmeal
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:226
#: input:226 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Cornmeal is produced in a mill out of corn and is one of three parts of the "
"Atlantean bread produced in bakeries."
msgstr ""
"La farina de blat de moro es produeix en un molí amb blat de moro i és una "
"de les tres parts del pa atlant produït a les fleques."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Blackroot
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:234
#: input:234 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Blackroots are a special kind of root produced at blackroot farms and "
"processed in mills. The Atlanteans like their strong taste and use their "
"flour for making bread."
msgstr ""
"Les arrels negres són un tipus especial d'arrel produïda a granges d'arrel "
"negra i processada en molins. Als atlants els agrada el seu gust fort i "
"utilitzen la seva farina per fer pa."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Blackroot Flour
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:243
#: input:243 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Blackroot Flour is produced in mills out of blackroots. It is used in "
"bakeries to make a tasty bread."
msgstr ""
"La farina d'arrels negres es produeix als molins a partir de les arrels "
"negres. S'utilitza a les fleques per fer un pa saborós."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Bread
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:252
#: input:252 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"This tasty bread is made in bakeries out of cornmeal, blackroot flour and "
"water. It is appreciated as basic food by miners, scouts and soldiers in "
"training sites (labyrinth, dungeon and temple)."
msgstr ""
"Aquest saborós pa s'elabora a les fleques amb farina de blat de moro, farina "
"d'arrel negra i aigua. És apreciat com a aliment bàsic per miners, "
"exploradors i soldats en llocs d'entrenament (laberint, calabós i temple)."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Quartz
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:264
#: input:264 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"These transparent quartz gems are used to build some exclusive buildings. "
"They are produced in crystal mines."
msgstr ""
"Aquestes gemmes de quars transparents s'utilitzen per construir alguns "
"edificis exclusius. Es produeixen a les mines de cristall."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Diamond
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:273
#: input:273 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"These wonderful diamonds are used to build some exclusive buildings. They "
"are mined in crystal mines."
msgstr ""
"Aquests meravellosos diamants s'utilitzen per construir alguns edificis "
"exclusius. S'extreuen en mines de cristall."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Coal, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:283
#: input:283 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Coal is mined in coal mines or produced out of logs by a charcoal kiln."
msgstr ""
"El carbó s'extrau de les mines i es produeix també amb troncs gràcies als "
"kilns de carbó vegetal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Coal, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:285
#: input:285 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"The Atlantean fires in smelting works, armor smithies and weapon smithies "
"are fed with coal."
msgstr ""
"Els focs atlants a les obres de fosa, les ferreries d'armadures i les "
"ferreries d'armes s'alimenten amb carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Iron Ore, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:296
#: input:296 standard
msgctxt "default_ware"
msgid "Iron ore is mined in iron mines."
msgstr "El mineral de ferro s'extreu a les mines de ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Iron Ore, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:298
#: input:298 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid "It is smelted in a smelting works to retrieve the iron."
msgstr "Es fon en una fosa per recuperar el ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Iron, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:309
#: input:309 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Iron is smelted out of iron ore."
msgstr "El ferro es fon amb mineral de ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Iron, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:311
#: input:311 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"It is produced by the smelting works and used in the toolsmithy, armor "
"smithy and weapon smithy."
msgstr ""
"És produït per les obres de fosa i s'utilitza a la ferreria d'eines, "
"ferreria d'armadures i ferreria d'armes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Gold Ore, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:322
#: input:322 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Gold ore is mined in a gold mine."
msgstr "El mineral d'or s'extreu en una mina d'or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Gold Ore, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:324
#: input:324 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Smelted in a smelting works, it turns into gold which is used as a precious "
"building material and to produce weapons and armor."
msgstr ""
"Fundida en una fosa, es converteix en or que s'utilitza com a material de "
"construcció preciós i per produir armes i armadures."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Gold, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:335
#: input:335 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid ""
"Gold is the most valuable of all metals, and it is smelted out of gold ore."
msgstr "L'or és el més valuós de tots els metalls, i es fon amb mineral d'or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Gold, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:337
#: input:337 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"It is produced by the smelting works and used by the armor smithy, the "
"weapon smithy and the gold spinning mill."
msgstr ""
"És produït per les obres de fosa i utilitzat per la ferreria d'armes, la "
"ferreria d'armes i la filatura d'or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Pick
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:348
#: input:348 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid ""
"Picks are used by stonecutters and miners. They are produced by the "
"toolsmith."
msgstr ""
"Els pics són utilitzats pels picapedrers i els miners. Són produïts pel "
"ferrer d'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Fire Tongs, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:358
#: input:358 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Fire tongs are the tools for smelting ores."
msgstr "Les pinces de foc són les eines per a la fosa de minerals."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Fire Tongs, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:360
#: input:360 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware_fire_tongs"
msgid "They are used in the smelting works and produced by the toolsmith."
msgstr "S'utilitzen en els treballs de fosa i els elabora l'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Saw
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:372
#: input:372 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"The saw is needed by the sawyer, the woodcutter and the toolsmith. It is "
"produced by the toolsmith."
msgstr ""
"La serra la necessiten el serrador, el llenyataire i el ferrer d'eines. Està "
"produït pel ferrer d'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Shovel, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:382
#: input:382 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Shovels are needed for the proper handling of plants."
msgstr "Les pales són necessàries per al bon maneig de les plantes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Shovel, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:384
#: input:384 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Therefore the forester and the blackroot farmer use them. They are produced "
"by the toolsmith."
msgstr ""
"Per tant, el silvicultor i l'agricultor d'arrel negra els utilitzen. Són "
"produïts pel ferrer d'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Hammer, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:395
#: input:395 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "The hammer is an essential tool."
msgstr "El martell és una eina essencial."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Hammer, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:397
#: input:397 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Geologists, builders, weaponsmiths, armorsmiths and shipwrights all need a "
"hammer. Make sure you’ve always got some in reserve! They are produced by "
"the toolsmith."
msgstr ""
"Geòlegs, constructors, armers, armers i constructors de vaixells necessiten "
"un martell. Assegureu-vos que sempre en teniu alguna reserva! Són produïts "
"pel ferrer d'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Spider Tongs
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:407
#: input:407 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Spider tongs are used by the spider breeder to handle the spiders. They are "
"produced by the toolsmith."
msgstr ""
"Les pinces d'aranya són utilitzades pel criador d'aranya per manejar les "
"aranyes. Són produïts pel ferrer d'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Fishing Net
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:416
#: input:416 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid "The fishing net is used by the fisher and produced by the toolsmith."
msgstr "La xarxa de pesca és utilitzada pel pescador i produïda pel ferrer."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Buckets
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:425
#: input:425 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid "Big buckets for the fish breeder – produced by the toolsmith."
msgstr "Cubells grans per al criador de peixos – produïts pel ferrer."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Hunting Bow
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:434
#: input:434 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"This bow is used by the Atlantean hunter. It is produced by the toolsmith."
msgstr ""
"Aquest arc és utilitzat pel caçador atlante. Està produït pel ferrer d'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Hook Pole
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:443
#: input:443 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"This hook pole is used by the smoker to suspend all the meat and fish from "
"the top of the smokery. It is created by the toolsmith."
msgstr ""
"Aquest ganxo l'utilitza el fumador per suspendre tota la carn i el peix de "
"la part superior del fumador. Està creat pel ferrer d'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Scythe, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:453
#: input:453 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "The scythe is the tool of the farmers."
msgstr "La dalla és l'eina dels pagesos."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Scythe, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:455
#: input:455 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid "Scythes are produced by the toolsmith."
msgstr "Les dalles les fa el ferrer d'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Bread Paddle, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:466
#: input:466 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "The bread paddle is the tool of the baker, each baker needs one."
msgstr "La paleta de pa és l'eina del forner, cada forner en necessita una."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Bread Paddle, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:468
#: input:468 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid "Bread paddles are produced by the toolsmith."
msgstr "Les paletes de pa són produïdes pel ferrer d'eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Light Trident
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:481
#: input:481 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"This is the basic weapon of the Atlantean soldiers. Together with a tabard, "
"it makes up the equipment of young soldiers. Light tridents are produced in "
"the weapon smithy as are all other tridents."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta és l'arma bàsica dels soldats atlants. Juntament amb un tabard, "
"constitueix l'equipament dels joves soldats. Els tridents lleugers es "
"produeixen a la ferreria d'armes com tots els altres tridents."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Long Trident
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:490
#: input:490 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"The long trident is the first trident in the training of soldiers. It is "
"produced in the weapon smithy and used in the dungeon – together with food – "
"to train soldiers from attack level 0 to level 1."
msgstr ""
"El trident llarg és el primer trident en l'entrenament dels soldats. Es "
"produeix a la ferreria d'armes i s'utilitza a la masmorra, juntament amb el "
"menjar, per entrenar soldats des del nivell d'atac 0 fins al nivell 1."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Steel Trident
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:499
#: input:499 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"This is the medium trident. It is produced in the weapon smithy and used by "
"advanced soldiers in the dungeon – together with food – to train from attack "
"level 1 to level 2."
msgstr ""
"Aquest és el trident mitjà. Es produeix a la ferreria d'armes i l'utilitzen "
"els soldats avançats a la masmorra, juntament amb el menjar, per entrenar "
"des del nivell d'atac 1 fins al nivell 2."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Diamond Double Trident
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:508
#: input:508 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"The diamond double trident is one of the best tridents produced by the "
"Atlantean weapon smithy. It is used in a dungeon – together with food – to "
"train soldiers from attack level 2 to level 3."
msgstr ""
"El doble trident de diamants és un dels millors tridents produïts per la "
"ferreria d'armes Atlante. S'utilitza en un calabós, juntament amb el menjar, "
"per entrenar soldats des del nivell d'atac 2 fins al nivell 3."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Heavy Double Trident
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:517
#: input:517 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"This is the most dangerous weapon of the Atlantean military. Only the best "
"of the best soldiers may use it. It is produced in the weapon smithy and "
"used in the dungeon – together with food – to train soldiers from attack "
"level 3 to level 4."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta és l'arma més perillosa de l'exèrcit atlant. Només els millors dels "
"millors soldats poden utilitzar-lo. Es produeix a la ferreria d'armes i "
"s'utilitza a la masmorra, juntament amb el menjar, per entrenar soldats des "
"del nivell d'atac 3 fins al nivell 4."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Steel Shield
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:526
#: input:526 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"This steel shield is produced in the armor smithy and used in the labyrinth "
"– together with food – to train soldiers from defense level 0 to level 1."
msgstr ""
"Aquest escut d'acer es produeix a la ferreria d'armadures i s'utilitza al "
"laberint, juntament amb el menjar, per entrenar soldats des del nivell de "
"defensa 0 fins al nivell 1."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Advanced Shield
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:535
#: input:535 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"These advanced shields are used by the best soldiers of the Atlanteans. They "
"are produced in the armor smithy and used in the labyrinth – together with "
"food – to train soldiers from defense level 1 to level 2."
msgstr ""
"Aquests escuts avançats són utilitzats pels millors soldats dels atlants. Es "
"produeixen a la ferreria d'armadures i s'utilitzen al laberint, juntament "
"amb el menjar, per entrenar soldats des del nivell de defensa 1 fins al "
"nivell 2."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Tabard
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:544
#: input:544 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"A tabard and a light trident are the basic equipment for young soldiers. "
"Tabards are produced in the weaving mill and used in the temple – together "
"with food – to improve soldiers’ health from level 0 to level 1."
msgstr ""
"Un tabard i un trident lleuger són l'equip bàsic dels joves soldats. Els "
"tabards es produeixen a la fàbrica de teixits i s'utilitzen al temple, "
"juntament amb el menjar, per millorar la salut dels soldats del nivell 0 al "
"nivell 1."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Gold Thread
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:553
#: input:553 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"This thread, made of gold by the gold spinning mill, is used for weaving the "
"exclusive golden tabard in the weaving mill."
msgstr ""
"Aquest fil, fet d'or per la filatura d'or, s'utilitza per teixir l'exclusiu "
"tabard daurat a la filatura."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean ware: Golden Tabard
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:562
#: input:562 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Golden tabards are produced in Atlantean weaving mills out of gold thread. "
"They are used in the temple – together with food – to improve soldiers’ "
"health from level 1 to level 2."
msgstr ""
"Els tabards d'or es produeixen a les fàbriques de teixit d'Atlantes amb fil "
"d'or. S'utilitzen al temple, juntament amb el menjar, per millorar la salut "
"dels soldats del nivell 1 al nivell 2."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Carrier
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:578
#: input:578 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Carries items along your roads."
msgstr "Porta objectes per les teves carreteres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Ferry
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:585
#: input:585 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Ships wares across narrow rivers."
msgstr "Envia mercaderies a través de rius estrets."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Horse
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:594
#: input:594 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid ""
"Horses help to carry items along busy roads. They are reared in a horse farm."
msgstr ""
"Els cavalls ajuden a transportar objectes per carreteres transitades. Es "
"crien en una granja de cavalls."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Horse Breeder
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:601
#: input:601 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid ""
"Breeds the strong Atlantean horses for adding them to the transportation "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Cria els forts cavalls atlantes per afegir-los al sistema de transport."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Stonecutter
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:611
#: input:611 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Cuts blocks of granite out of rocks in the vicinity."
msgstr "Talla blocs de granit de les roques dels voltants."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Woodcutter
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:618
#: input:618 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Fells trees."
msgstr "Talla arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Sawyer
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:625
#: input:625 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Saws logs to produce planks."
msgstr "Serra troncs per produir taulons."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Forester
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:632
#: input:632 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Plants trees."
msgstr "Planta arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Builder
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:639
#: input:639 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Works at construction sites to raise new buildings."
msgstr "Treballs en obres per aixecar nous edificis."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean female worker: Spider Breeder
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:646
#: input:646 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Breeds spiders for silk."
msgstr "Cria aranyes per a la seda."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Weaver
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:653
#: input:653 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Produces spidercloth for buildings, ships and soldiers."
msgstr "Produeix tela d'aranya per a edificis, vaixells i soldats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Shipwright
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:660
#: input:660 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Works at the shipyard and constructs new ships."
msgstr "Treballa a la drassana i construeix nous vaixells."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Fisher
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:670
#: input:670 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "The fisher fishes delicious fish and collects seashels."
msgstr "El pescador pesca peixos deliciosos i recull peixes marines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Fish Breeder
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:677
#: input:677 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Breeds fish."
msgstr "Cria peixos."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Hunter
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:684
#: input:684 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "The hunter brings fresh, raw meat to the colonists."
msgstr "El caçador porta carn fresca i crua als colons."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Smoker
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:691
#: input:691 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Smokes meat and fish."
msgstr "Fuma carn i peix."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Farmer
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:698
#: input:698 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Plants and harvests cornfields."
msgstr "Planta i collia camps de blat de moro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Blackroot Farmer
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:705
#: input:705 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Plants and harvests blackroot."
msgstr "Planta i recull arrel negre."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Miller
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:712
#: input:712 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid ""
"Grinds blackroots and corn to produce blackroot flour and cornmeal, "
"respectively."
msgstr ""
"Tritura les arrels negres i el blat de moro per produir farina d'arrel negra "
"i farina de blat de moro, respectivament."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Baker
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:719
#: input:719 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Bakes bread for workers."
msgstr "Cuina pa per als treballadors."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Geologist
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:729
#: input:729 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Discovers resources for mining."
msgstr "Descobreix recursos per a la mineria."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Miner
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:736
#: input:736 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Works deep in the mines to obtain coal, iron, gold or precious stones."
msgstr ""
"Treballa en profunditat a les mines per obtenir carbó, ferro, or o pedres "
"precioses."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Charcoal Burner
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:743
#: input:743 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Burns coal."
msgstr "Crema carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Smelter
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:750
#: input:750 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Smelts ores into metal."
msgstr "Fon els minerals en metall."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Toolsmith
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:758
#: input:758 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Produces tools for the workers."
msgstr "Produeix eines per als treballadors."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Recruit
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:768
#: input:768 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Eager to become a soldier and defend his tribe!"
msgstr "Amb ganes de convertir-se en soldat i defensar la seva tribu!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Soldier
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:777
#: input:777 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Defend and Conquer!"
msgstr "Defensa i venç!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Trainer
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:784
#: input:784 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Trains the soldiers."
msgstr "Entrena els soldats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Priestess
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:791
#: input:791 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Works in the temple and improves soldiers in ‘Health’."
msgstr "Treballa al temple i millora els soldats en 'Salut'."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Priestess
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:793
#: input:793 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid ""
"The priestess has to pray to the God Lutas on a shore. Make sure she has "
"free access to water. Lutas is showing her his favour when a seashell "
"appears on the cost. This seashell can be collected by a fisher for meat "
"later."
msgstr ""
"La sacerdotessa ha de resar al Déu Lutas a la riba. Assegureu-vos que tingui "
"accés gratuït a l'aigua. En Lutas li està mostrant el seu favor quan apareix "
"una petxina marina al cost. Aquesta petxina la pot recollir més tard un "
"pescador per a la carn."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Weaponsmith
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:800
#: input:800 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Produces weapons for the soldiers."
msgstr "Produeix armes per als soldats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Armorsmith
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:807
#: input:807 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid "Produces armor for the soldiers."
msgstr "Produeix armadures per als soldats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean worker: Scout
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:814
#: input:814 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_worker"
msgid ""
"Scouts like Scotty the scout scouting unscouted areas in a scouty fashion."
msgstr ""
"Escoltes com Scotty l'escolta explorant àrees no explorades d'una manera "
"exploradora."

