#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:839
#: input:832 input:839 standard
msgid ""
"Fishers can collect this type of seashells for meat. They appear on shores "
"around temple when priestess prays to the God Lutas before improving "
"soldiers health."
msgstr ""
"Els pescadors poden recollir aquest tipus de petxines per a la carn. "
"Apareixen a les costes al voltant del temple quan la sacerdotessa prega al "
"Déu Lutas abans de millorar la salut dels soldats."

