#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean resource indicator: Coal, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:940
#: input:940 standard
msgid "There is only a little bit of coal here."
msgstr "Aquí només hi ha una mica de carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean resource indicator: Iron, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:949
