#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean resource indicator: Gold, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:960
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1004
