msgstr "Aquí només hi ha una mica d'or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean resource indicator: Stones, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:971
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1015
#: input:971 input:1015 standard
msgid ""
"Precious stones are used in the construction of big buildings. They can be "
"dug up by a crystal mine. You will also get granite from the mine."
msgstr ""
"Les pedres precioses s'utilitzen en la construcció de grans edificis. Poden "
"ser excavats per una mina de cristall. També obtindreu granit de la mina."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean resource indicator: Stones, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:973
#: input:973 standard
