msgstr "Aquí hi ha molt carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean resource indicator: Iron, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:995
#: input:995 standard
