msgstr "Aquí hi ha molt ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean resource indicator: Gold, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1006
#: input:1006 standard
msgid "There is a lot of gold here."
msgstr "Aquí hi ha molt or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean resource indicator: Stones, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1017
#: input:1017 standard
msgid "There are many precious stones here."
msgstr "Aquí hi ha moltes pedres precioses."

