msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Carves precious (and normal) stones out of the rock in mountain terrain."
msgstr "Talla pedres precioses (i normals) de la roca en terrenys de muntanya."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Atlantean production site: Low Crystal Mine
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1596
#: input:1596 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"No, no, there is no need to build a deep mine. This low mine ensures a quick "
"supply of sufficient amount of the hardest diamonds for our double tridents."
msgstr ""
"No, no, no cal construir una mina profunda. Aquesta mina baixa garanteix un "
"subministrament ràpid de quantitat suficient dels diamants més durs per als "
"nostres dobles tridents."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Atlantean production site: Low Crystal Mine
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1598
#: input:1598 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"An impatient trainer can’t wait to receive his first double trident delivery"
msgstr ""
"Un entrenador impacient no pot esperar per rebre el seu primer lliurament de "
"doble trident"

