#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1627
#: input:1600 input:1627 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If this building is fully supplied and all minerals are needed by the "
"economy, production of one granite takes %1$s, one quartz takes %2$s and one "
"diamond takes %3$s on average. If only one kind of mineral is needed by the "
"economy, production of one granite takes %4$s, one quartz takes %5$s and one "
"diamond takes %6$s on average."
msgstr ""
"Si aquest edifici està completament proveït i l'economia necessita tots els "
"minerals, la producció d'un granit necessita %1$s, un quars necessita %2$s i "
"un diamant necessita %3$s de mitjana. Si l'economia només necessita un tipus "
"de mineral, la producció d'un granit necessita %4$s, un quars necessita %5$s "
"i un diamant necessita %6$s de mitjana."

