#: input:1607 input:1666 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Digs gold ore out of the ground in mountain terrain."
msgstr "Excava mineral d'or del sòl en terrenys de muntanya."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Atlantean production site: Low Gold Mine
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1609
#: input:1609 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"We Atlanteans are very proud of our weaving abilities and we are especially "
"proud of our golden tabards. That is why a quick supply of gold into our "
"spinning mills is question of honour for us."
msgstr ""
"Els atlants estem molt orgullosos de les nostres habilitats de teixir i "
"estem especialment orgullosos dels nostres tabards d'or. És per això que un "
"subministrament ràpid d'or a les nostres filatures és una qüestió d'honor "
"per a nosaltres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Atlantean production site: Low Gold Mine
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1611
#: input:1611 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "A priestess is ashamed by not having golden tabards for soldiers"
msgstr ""
"Una sacerdotessa s'avergonyeix de no tenir tabardes d'or per als soldats"

