msgid ""
"‘Way down here in this deep mine<br>where the sun it dare not shine,<br>I "
"sweat and toil till day is done,<br>but I’ll be back with morning come.’"
msgstr ""
"\"Aquí baix, en aquesta mina profunda<br>on el sol no s'atreveix a brillar,"
"<br>Suo i treballo fins que s'acaba el dia,<br>però tornaré quan arribi el "
"matí.\""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Gold Mine
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1668
#: input:1668 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"‘Way down here in these golden grounds<br>with stones above us the thousand "
"pounds<br>I dig in the dust until I see the spark;<br>The golden ore I find "
"in the dark.’"
msgstr ""
"\"Aquí baix, en aquests terrenys daurats<br>amb pedres per sobre nostre les "
"mil lliures<br>Excava la pols fins que veig l'espurna;<br>El mineral daurat "
"que trobo a la foscor.\""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Gold Mine
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1673
#: input:1673 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Miner’s prayer"
msgstr "Pregària del miner"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean training site: Dungeon, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1685
#: input:1685 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Trains soldiers in ‘Attack’."
msgstr "Entrena soldats a \"Atac\"."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean training site: Dungeon, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1687
#: input:1687 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Equips the soldiers with all necessary weapons."
msgstr "Equipa els soldats amb totes les armes necessàries."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Dungeon
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1690
#: input:1690 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Make our enemies feel the pain, so enter here to gain your train!"
msgstr ""
"Fes que els nostres enemics sentin el dolor, així que entra aquí per guanyar "
"el teu tren!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Dungeon
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1692
#: input:1692 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Engraving on the entrance to the dungeon"
msgstr "Gravat a l'entrada del calabós"

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean training site: Dungeon, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1695
#: input:1695 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If all needed wares are delivered in time, a dungeon can train one soldier "
"one level in attack in %s on average."
msgstr ""
"Si totes les mercaderies necessàries s'entreguen a temps, un calabós pot "
"entrenar un soldat un nivell d'atac a %s de mitjana."

