msgid "Complete training of one soldier takes %s on average."
msgstr "L'entrenament complet d'un soldat requereix %s de mitjana."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean training site: Labyrinth, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1706
#: input:1706 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Trains soldiers in ‘Defense’ and ‘Evade’."
msgstr "Entrena soldats a \"Defensa\" i \"Evadir\"."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean training site: Labyrinth, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1708
#: input:1708 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Equips the soldiers with all necessary weapons and armor parts."
msgstr "Equipa els soldats amb totes les armes i peces d'armadura necessàries."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Labyrinth
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1711
#: input:1711 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Our enemies claim: we have a ruddy twisted way to fight. Check the way we "
"train, in this labyrinth they may be right."
msgstr ""
"Els nostres enemics afirmen: tenim una manera de lluitar retorçada. "
"Comproveu com entrenem, en aquest laberint poden tenir raó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Labyrinth
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1714
#: input:1714 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Atlantean hero after first contact with a real enemy"
msgstr "Heroi atlant després del primer contacte amb un enemic real"

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean training site: Labyrinth, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1717
#: input:1717 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If all needed wares are delivered in time, a labyrinth can train one soldier "
"one level in defense or evade in %s on average."
msgstr ""
"Si totes les mercaderies necessàries es lliuren a temps, un laberint pot "
"entrenar un soldat un nivell en defensa o evadir-se a %s de mitjana."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Temple
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1727
#: input:1727 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Improves soldiers in ‘Health’."
msgstr "Millora els soldats en \"Salut\"."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Temple
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1729
#: input:1729 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"The priestess has to pray to the God Lutas on a shore. Make sure she has "
"free access to water. Lutas is showing her his favour when a seashell "
"appears on the cost. This seashell can be collected by a fisher for meat."
msgstr ""
"La sacerdotessa ha de resar al Déu Lutas a la riba. Assegureu-vos que tingui "
"accés gratuït a l'aigua. En Lutas li està mostrant el seu favor quan apareix "
"una petxina marina al cost. Aquesta petxina la pot recollir un pescador de "
"carn."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean training site: Temple
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1731
#: input:1731 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "She spells seashells on the seashore of shallow sea. S-E-A-S-H-E-L-L-S."
msgstr ""
"Encantera petxines marines a la vora del mar de poca profunditat. S-E-A-S-H-"
"E-L-L-S."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Temple
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1733
#: input:1733 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "An Atlantean spell, which is to be repeated ten times in quick pace"
msgstr "Un encanteri atlant, que s'ha de repetir deu vegades a ritme ràpid"

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Temple, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1736
#: input:1736 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If all needed wares are delivered in time, a temple needs between %1$s and "
"%2$s to train one soldier one level in health, depending on how far the "
"priestess has to walk."
msgstr ""
"Si totes les mercaderies necessàries s'entreguen a temps, un temple "
"necessita entre %1$s i %2$s per entrenar un soldat d'un nivell de salut, "
"depenent de la distància que hagi de caminar la sacerdotessa."

