#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1766
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1779
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1793
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1807
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1823
#: input:1752 input:1766 input:1779 input:1793 input:1807 input:1823 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If you’re low on soldiers to occupy new military sites, use the downward "
"arrow button to decrease the capacity. You can also click on a soldier to "
"send him away."
msgstr ""
"Si teniu pocs soldats per ocupar nous llocs militars, feu servir el botó de "
"fletxa cap avall per reduir la capacitat. També podeu fer clic a un soldat "
"per enviar-lo."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Guard
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1755
#: input:1755 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Hey soldier, even if this is the smallest of our military buildings you "
"still must not sleep all day!"
msgstr ""
"Hola soldat, encara que aquest sigui el més petit dels nostres edificis "
"militars, encara no has de dormir tot el dia!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Guard
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1757
#: input:1757 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Officer visiting a remote guard"
msgstr "Oficial visitant un guàrdia remot"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Big Guardhall
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1768
#: input:1768 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "In this hall we praise the fight, for God’s honour day and night."
msgstr "En aquesta sala lloem la lluita, per l'honor de Déu dia i nit."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Big Guardhall
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1770
#: input:1770 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Scribbling on the wall of a big guardhall"
msgstr "Gargotejant a la paret d'una gran sala de guàrdia"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Low Tower
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1781
#: input:1781 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"With three soldiers we can achieve an optimal balance between military power "
"and building cost."
msgstr ""
"Amb tres soldats podem aconseguir un equilibri òptim entre la potència "
"militar i el cost de construcció."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Low Tower
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1783
#: input:1783 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Notes on the building instructions"
msgstr "Notes sobre les instruccions de construcció"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Round Tower
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1795
#: input:1795 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"All the other tribes envy us for our towers, elegant outside, comfortable "
"inside, still perfect for defense."
msgstr ""
"Totes les altres tribus ens envegen per les nostres torres, elegants per "
"fora, còmodes per dins, encara perfectes per a la defensa."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Round Tower
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1797
#: input:1797 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Soldier handing over his duties to a younger one"
msgstr "Soldat cedint els seus deures a un més jove"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Cone Shaped Tower
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1810
#: input:1810 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Beware our mighty high towers! From the topmost spot we can see wide into "
"the lands and spot the enemy far away."
msgstr ""
"Compte amb les nostres poderoses torres altes! Des del punt més alt podem "
"veure amples les terres i veure l'enemic lluny."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Cone Shaped Tower
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1813
#: input:1813 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Soldier showing off a cone shaped tower"
msgstr "Soldat mostrant una torre en forma de con"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Diamond Castle
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1826
#: input:1826 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Sometimes even we Atlanteans need to use brute force, but we always play it "
"wisely."
msgstr ""
"De vegades, fins i tot els atlants necessitem utilitzar la força bruta, però "
"sempre hi juguem amb prudència."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Diamond Castle
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1828
#: input:1828 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "‘Wisdom of the Fight’ by the warriors’ guild"
msgstr "‘La saviesa de la lluita’ del gremi de guerrers"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Ferry Yard
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1837
#: input:1837 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Builds ferries."
msgstr "Construeix ferris."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Ferry Yard, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1840
#: input:1840 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Needs water nearby. Be aware ferries carry wares only, no workers."
msgstr ""
"Necessita aigua a prop. Tingueu en compte que els ferris només porten "
"mercaderies, sense treballadors."

